text: My sweet Angel, Jimin!!! Thank you for being in my life!!! With your beautiful songs and your magical, charming voice, you save me every day without knowing it!!! But you are so far away, beckoning me with your gentle Angel voice, and if I fall, I rise from my knees and follow you into my wonderful future!!! Thanks to you, even after the most severe thunderstorm, a beautiful rainbow appears in my soul and the warm sun shines!!! I can't express in words all my gratitude to you and the guys!!!After all, you are coloring my world with the brightest colors and thanks to you, I can paint a picture of my life from a blank sheet!!! I love you all very much and look forward to your reunion!!!
